<p>Hi <%= user.email %>!</p>

<p>You recently requested to reset your password for your <%= ENV["SYSTEM_APP_NAME"] %> account. Use the link below to reset it. <strong>This password reset is only valid for the next <%= ENV["HOURS_PASSWORD_RESET_LINK_EXPIRES_AFTER"] || 6 %> hours.</strong></p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(user, reset_password_token: token) %></p>

<p>
  If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact <%= mail_to("#{ENV["SYSTEM_EMAIL"]}", "support", subject: "#{ENV["SYSTEM_APP_NAME"]} PASSWORD RESET CONCERN") %> if you have questions.
</p>

<p>Thank you,</p>
<p><%= ENV["SYSTEM_APP_NAME"] %></p>
